@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-5 text-light">
    <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h1 class="display-4 text-primary">Welcome to Bakar Lake Resort</h1>
            <p class="lead">A peaceful getaway located on the shores of the beautiful Chotiari Dam in Sanghar District, Sindh, Pakistan.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="text-center text-light">Our Location</h2>
            <p class="text-white">Bakar Lake Resort is about 35 kilometers from Sanghar town, set against the backdrop of the Achhro Thar (White Desert). The Chotiari Dam, completed in December 2002, serves as an important water reservoir and a haven for diverse wildlife. The area is known for its tranquil waters, stunning sunsets, and rich biodiversity, making it an ideal destination for nature lovers and travelers seeking peace.</p>
            <p class="text-white">The Chotiari Dam is a vital piece of infrastructure, not just providing water storage for the region, but also being a scenic natural landmark that attracts visitors looking to connect with nature.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="text-center text-light">Our Offerings</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card bg-dark text-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-center">Boating Adventures</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Explore the expansive waters of Chotiari Dam with our guided boat tours, offering a unique perspective of the reservoir and its surroundings.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card bg-dark text-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-center">Cultural Experiences</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Immerse yourself in the local culture and history of the region, with opportunities to visit nearby historical sites and engage with the local community.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="card bg-dark text-light mb-3">
                <div class="card-header bg-primary text-center">Culinary Delights</div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Savor traditional Sindhi cuisine at our on-site restaurant, featuring specialties such as Saji Kofta and Fish Halwa.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5 text-center">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <a href="@Url.Action("SendMessage", "Contact")" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Contact Us</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-12">
            <h2 class="text-center text-light">About Chotiari Dam</h2>
            <p class="text-white">Chotiari Dam, located in the Sanghar District of Sindh, Pakistan, is an artificial water reservoir that serves as a crucial source of water storage for irrigation and flood control in the region. Completed in December 2002, the dam spans an area of approximately 24,300 acres and has a storage capacity of 750,000 acre-feet.</p>
            <p class="text-white">Before the construction of the reservoir, this site was home to a few natural lakes, fed by the tributaries of the Nara Canal. The area is also a wetland and habitat for birds, reptiles, and small mammals. Now, the environment and wildlife of this area are affected by the saline water discharge of the Left Bank Outfall Drain (LBOD).</p>
            <p class="text-white">The dam is not only a vital infrastructure project but also a stunning natural landmark. Its serene, expansive waters are surrounded by the peaceful landscape of the Achhro Thar (White Desert), making it an ideal destination for nature lovers, bird watchers, and adventure enthusiasts.</p>
            <p class="text-white">Chotiari Dam is also known for its rich biodiversity, attracting a variety of bird species, especially migratory birds. The area around the dam is a haven for wildlife, including fish and other aquatic life, making it an excellent spot for fishing and boating.</p>
            <p class="text-white">The breathtaking beauty of the dam, coupled with its tranquil environment, offers a peaceful escape from the hustle of daily life. It is a place where visitors can unwind, enjoy scenic views, and experience the natural wonders of the region.</p>
            <p class="text-white">At Bakar Lake Resort, situated along the banks of Chotiari Dam, guests can enjoy boat tours on the reservoir, which provide a unique view of the surrounding landscape and an opportunity to witness the dam's awe-inspiring beauty.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
